<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.1">
<l>kaimmāṉa matayāṉai yiṭartīrtta karumukilai</l>
<l>maimmāṉa maṇiyai yaṇikoḷ marakatattai</l>
<l>yemmāṉai yempirā ṉaiyīca ṉaiyeṉmaṉattuḷ</l>
<l>ammāṉai yaṭiyē ṉaṭaintuyn tupōṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking refuge in the dark cloud who removed the suffering</l>
<l>Of the rutting elephant with a hand-like [trunk], the kohl-like jewel,</l>
<l>Beauty-bearing emerald, our lord, our master, god,</l>
<l>The lord within my heart, I, his servant, was finally saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
